name: deepseek-code
description: Complete multi-agent system for DeepSeek Code. V3.2: auto-select model (deepseek-reasoner for complex code), thinking mode, smart template chunking, scalable pool (2-10 instances), adaptive max_tokens. Plus: oneshot delegation, quantum parallel, multi-session, conversational dialogue, surgical memory, global memory, adaptive prompts, and 3-phase collaboration protocol. Claude Code orchestrates DeepSeek as a 1M-token code generation engine.
